\section{Discussion}
\begin{frame}{Discussion}
    \begin{itemize}
        \item The results obtained with this analysis on \texttt{R} are in line with the real situation;
       \pause \item All the ecological indexes analysed (NDVI, NDMI, FCOVER) showed a better situation in year 2015 rather than in year 2023;
       \pause \item There is a strong need for ecosystem restoration in Salento peninsula;
       \pause \item Salento has to become a case study as example of ecological collapse: we can learn from our mistakes and do \boldsymbol{not} do them again! 
    \end{itemize}
\end{frame}

